## ðŸ“Œ Overview  
This project provides an investigation into a **supply chain attack** targeting a third-party vendor whose compromised software update impacted downstream clients.  
The report analyzes the breach, identifies root causes, evaluates organizational exposure, and recommends strengthened vendor-management controls.

The full report is included in this folder.

