---

## ðŸ§  Summary  
This investigation highlights how organizations inherit risk from external vendors.  
The assignment covers:  
- How the malicious update was introduced  
- What internal controls failed  
- Which stakeholders were affected  
- How downstream systems became vulnerable  

The report also provides corrective actions focused on vendor auditing, code integrity checks, contractual controls, and continuous monitoring.

